<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.6">
<l>cinturami laṅkataṉ tiruneṟ ṟimēl</l>
<l rend="indent">tiruttiya kōṟampun tirukku ḻalu</l>
<l>mantaramu ḻavattaṇta ḻaikkā viṉkīḻ</l>
<l rend="indent">varumā yarōṭuṭaṉ vaḷaikōl vīca</l>
<l>vantamoṉ ṟillāta vāyap piḷḷai</l>
<l rend="indent">yaṟintaṟin tivvīti pōtu mākil</l>
<l>pantukoṇ ṭāṉeṉṟu vaḷaittu vaittup</l>
<l rend="indent">pavaḷavāy muṟuvalum kāṇpōm tōḻī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Knowing this and that about the limitless herder boy,</l>
<l rend="indent">if he passes through this street,</l>
<l>with a properly applied tilaka on his holy forehead</l>
<l rend="indent">so that it shines, holy curls, and a holy forehead ornament,</l>
<l>coming along with the herders under the forest of cool leaves,</l>
<l rend="indent">[playing] a heavenly drum,</l>
<l>while [he] swings his crooked stick [around],</l>
<l>[we will] surround and detain [him] saying “he took [our] ball,”</l>
<l>[and in this way,] friend, we will see the smile upon [his] coral[-red] lips.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
